#: ../../boot_options.rst:2
msgid "Boot options"
msgstr "Mogućnosti pokretanja"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:4
msgid ""
"Some graphics cards and motherboards don't work well with the open-source "
"drivers present in Linux Mint by default."
msgstr ""
"Određene grafičke kartice i matične ploče ne rade dobro s upravljačkim "
"programima otvorenog kôda zadanim u Linux Mintu."

#: ../../boot_options.rst:7
msgid "Compatibility mode"
msgstr "Kompatibilan način rada"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:9
msgid ""
"The easiest option is to select ``compatibility mode`` from the USB stick "
"(or DVD) boot menu."
msgstr ""
"Najjednostavnije je odabrati stavku  ``compatibility mode`` iz izbornika "
"pokretanja USB uređaja (ili DVD-a)."

#: ../../boot_options.rst:15
msgid "Grub menu (EFI mode)"
msgstr "Grub izbornik (EFI način)"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:21
msgid "Isolinux menu (BIOS mode)"
msgstr "Isolinux izbornik (BIOS način)"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:23
msgid "If that doesn't work, you can try the ``nomodeset`` boot option."
msgstr "Ako to ne radi, možete probati ``nomodeset`` mogućnost pokretanja."

#: ../../boot_options.rst:26
msgid "Nomodeset boot option"
msgstr "Nomodeset mogućnost pokretanja"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:28
msgid ""
"In EFI mode, highlight the ``Start Linux Mint`` option and press :kbd:`e` to "
"modify the boot options."
msgstr ""
"U EFI načinu, odaberite ``Pokreni Linux Mint`` stavku i pritisnite :kbd:`e` "
"za promjenu mogućnosti pokretanja."

#: ../../boot_options.rst:34
msgid ""
"Replace ``quiet splash`` with ``nomodeset`` and press :kbd:`F10` to boot."
msgstr ""
"Zamijenite ``quiet splash`` sa ``nomodeset`` i pritisnite :kbd:`F10` za "
"pokretanje."

#: ../../boot_options.rst:36
msgid ""
"In BIOS mode, highlight ``Start Linux Mint`` and press :kbd:`Tab` to modify "
"the boot options."
msgstr ""
"U BIOS načinu, odaberite ``Pokreni Linux Mint`` stavku i pritisnite "
":kbd:`Tab` za promjenu mogućnosti pokretanja."

#: ../../boot_options.rst:42
msgid ""
"Replace ``quiet splash`` with ``nomodeset`` and press :kbd:`Enter` to boot."
msgstr ""
"Zamijenite ``quiet splash`` sa ``nomodeset`` i pritisnite :kbd:`Enter` za "
"pokretanje."

#: ../../boot_options.rst:45
msgid ""
"Repeat this operation post-install in your grub boot menu and read "
":doc:`drivers` to install additional drivers."
msgstr ""
"Ponovite ovu radnju nakon instalacije u grub izborniku pokretanja i "
"pročitajte :doc:`drivers` za instalaciju dodatnih upravljačkih programa."

#: ../../boot_options.rst:48
msgid "Other boot options"
msgstr "Ostale mogućnosti pokretanja"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:50
msgid "If you still cannot boot try one of the following solutions:"
msgstr ""
"Ako još uvijek ne možete pokrenuti sustav pokušajte jedno od sljedećih "
"rješenja:"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:52
msgid "Try ``nouveau.noaccel=1`` instead of ``nomodeset``."
msgstr "Pokušajte sa ``nouveau.noaccel=1`` umjesto ``nomodeset``."

#: ../../boot_options.rst:53
msgid ""
"After the installation, use :menuselection:`Advanced Options --> Recovery "
"mode` from the boot menu and choose ``resume``."
msgstr ""
"Nakon instalacije, koristite :menuselection:`Napredne mogućnosti --> "
"Oporavak sustava` u izborniku pokretanja i odaberite ``nastavi``."

#: ../../boot_options.rst:56
msgid "Install an older release"
msgstr "Instalacija starijeg izdanja"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:58
msgid ""
"If your computer has compatibility issues with the latest Linux Mint "
"release, install a previous release from the same Linux Mint series."
msgstr ""
"Ako vaše računalo ima problema s kompatibilnošću Linux Mint izdanja, "
"instalirajte prijašnje izdanje iste Linux Mint serije."

#: ../../boot_options.rst:60
msgid ""
"For instance, if you can't install Linux Mint 18.3 (which comes with a 4.10 "
"kernel), install Linux Mint 18 (which comes with a 4.4 kernel) and upgrade "
"to 18.3."
msgstr ""
"Na primjer, ako ne možete instalirati Linux Mint 18.3 (koji dolazi sa 4.10 "
"kernelom), instalirajte Linux Mint 18 (koji dolazi sa 4.4 kernelom) i "
"nadogradite na 18.3."

#: ../../boot_options.rst:63
msgid ""
"The first release in each series uses an LTS (Long Term Support) kernel. "
"Upgrading from this release to the latest one in the series does not change "
"your kernel."
msgstr ""
"Prvo izdanje u svakoj seriji koristi LTS (Dugoročno podržani) kernel. "
"Nadogradnja s tog izdanja na najnovije u seriji ne zamjenjuje vaš kernel."

#: ../../boot.rst:2
msgid "Boot Linux Mint"
msgstr "Pokretanje Linux Minta"

#: ../../boot.rst:4
msgid ""
"Now that you have Linux Mint on a USB stick (or DVD) boot the computer from "
"it."
msgstr ""
"Pošto imate Linux Mint na USB uređaju (ili DVD-u) pokrenite računalo s njega."

#: ../../boot.rst:6
msgid "Insert your USB stick (or DVD) into the computer."
msgstr "Umetnite USB uređaj (ili DVD) u vaše računalo."

#: ../../boot.rst:8 ../../drivers.rst:23 ../../efi.rst:61 ../../oem.rst:21
msgid "Restart the computer."
msgstr "Ponovno pokrenite računalo"

#: ../../boot.rst:10
msgid ""
"Before your computer boots your current operating system (Windows, Mac, "
"Linux) you should see your `BIOS <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BIOS>`_ "
"loading screen. Check the screen or your computer's documentation to know "
"which key to press and instruct your computer to boot on USB (or DVD)."
msgstr ""
"Prije nego što računalo pokrene vaš operativni sustav (Windows, Mac, Linux) "
"trebali bi vidjeti vaš `BIOS <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BIOS>`_ zaslon "
"učitavanja. Provjerite zaslon ili vašu dokumentaciju računala kako bi "
"saznali koju tipku treba pritisnuti za pokretanje računala sa USB uređaja "
"(ili DVD-a)."

#: ../../boot.rst:13
msgid ""
"Most BIOS have a special key you can press to select the boot device and all "
"of them have a special key to enter the BIOS configuration screen (from "
"which you can define the boot order). Depending on the BIOS, these special "
"keys can be :kbd:`Escape`, :kbd:`F1`, :kbd:`F2`, :kbd:`F8`, :kbd:`F10`, "
":kbd:`F11`, :kbd:`F12`, or :kbd:`Delete`. That information is usually "
"briefly written on the screen during the boot sequence."
msgstr ""
"Većina BIOS-a ima određenu tipku koju možete pritisnuti za odabir uređaja "
"pokretanja a svaki od njih ima posebnu tipku za ulazak u BIOS zaslon "
"podešavanja  (iz kojega možete odrediti poredak pokretanja uređaja). Ovisno "
"o BIOSU, te određene tipke mogu biti :kbd:`Escape`, :kbd:`F1`, :kbd:`F2`, "
":kbd:`F8`, :kbd:`F10`, :kbd:`F11`, :kbd:`F12`, ili :kbd:`Delete`. Ta "
"informacija je kratko prikazana na zaslonu tijekom postupka pokretanja."

#: ../../boot.rst:16
msgid ""
"On Macs, keep your finger pressed on the :kbd:`Alt` or :kbd:`Option` key "
"after hearing the boot sound."
msgstr ""
"Na Macovima, držite pritisnutu :kbd:`Alt` ili :kbd:`Option` tipku nakon što "
"čujete zvuk pokretanja."

#: ../../boot.rst:18
msgid ""
"The Linux Mint ISO can be booted both in EFI or BIOS mode. In EFI mode it "
"shows a grub menu. In BIOS mode it shows an isolinux menu."
msgstr ""
"Linux Mint ISO može se pokrenuti u oba načina, EFI ili BIOS. U EFI načinu "
"prikazuje grub izbornik. U BIOS načinu prikazuje isolinux izbornik."

#: ../../boot.rst:24
msgid "The isolinux menu in BIOS mode"
msgstr "Isolinux izbornik u BIOS načinu"

#: ../../boot.rst:30
msgid "The grub menu in EFI mode"
msgstr "Grub izbornik u EFI načinu"

#: ../../boot.rst:32
msgid ""
"From one of these menu, press :kbd:`Enter` to start Linux Mint from your USB "
"stick (or DVD)."
msgstr ""
"U jednom od tih izbornika, pritisnite :kbd:`Enter` za pokretanje Linux Minta "
"sa USB uređaja (ili DVD-a)."

#: ../../burn.rst:2
msgid "Create the bootable media"
msgstr "Stvaranje medija za pokretanje sustava"

#: ../../burn.rst:4
msgid "The easiest way to install Linux Mint is with a USB stick."
msgstr "Najjednostavniji način instalacije Linux Minta je sa USB uređaja."

#: ../../burn.rst:6
msgid "If you cannot boot from USB, you can use a blank DVD."
msgstr "Ako ne možete pokrenuti sa USB uređaja, možete koristiti prazan DVD."

#: ../../burn.rst:9
msgid "How to make a bootable USB stick"
msgstr "Kako napraviti USB uređaj za pokretanje sustava"

#: ../../burn.rst:12
msgid "In Linux Mint"
msgstr "U Linux Mintu"

#: ../../burn.rst:14
msgid ""
"Right-click the ISO file and select :menuselection:`Make Bootable USB "
"Stick`, or launch :menuselection:`Menu --> Accessories --> USB Image Writer`."
msgstr ""
"Desno kliknite na ISO datoteku i odaberite :menuselection:`Napravi USB "
"uređaj za pokretanje sustava`, ili pokrenite :menuselection:`Izbornik --> "
"Pomagala --> USB zapisnik slika`."

#: ../../burn.rst:20
msgid "Select your USB device and click :guilabel:`Write`."
msgstr "Odaberite svoj USB uređaj i kliknite :guilabel:`Zapiši`."

#: ../../burn.rst:23
msgid "In Windows, Mac OS, or other Linux distributions"
msgstr "U Windowsima, Mac OS-u, ili drugim Linux distribucijama"

#: ../../burn.rst:25
msgid ""
"Download `Etcher <https://www.balena.io/etcher/>`_, install it and run it."
msgstr ""
"Preuzmite `Etcher <https://www.balena.io/etcher/>`_, instalirajte ga i "
"pokrenite."

#: ../../burn.rst:31
msgid "Using Etcher"
msgstr "Korištenje Etchera"

#: ../../burn.rst:33
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Select image` and select your ISO file."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Select image` i odaberite svoju ISO datoteku."

#: ../../burn.rst:35
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Select drive` and select your USB stick."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Select drive` i odaberite svoj USB uređaj."

#: ../../burn.rst:37
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Flash!`."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Flash!`."

#: ../../burn.rst:41
msgid "How to make a bootable DVD"
msgstr "Kako napraviti DVD za pokretanje sustava"

#: ../../burn.rst:43
msgid "Optical discs are slow and burning to disc is prone to errors."
msgstr "Optički diskovi su spori i snimanje diska je sklono greškama."

#: ../../burn.rst:46
msgid "To prevent issues, burn at the lowest possible speed."
msgstr "Kako bi spriječili probleme, snimajte na najsporijoj brzini."

#: ../../burn.rst:49
msgid ""
"Burn the content of the ISO onto the DVD, not the ISO file itself. When "
"finished, your DVD should contain directories such as ``boot`` and "
"``casper``, it shouldn't be an empty DVD containing an .iso file."
msgstr ""
"Snimite sadržaj ISO datoteke na DVD, a ne samu ISO datoteku. Kada završite "
"snimanje, vaš DVD bi trebao sadržavati direktorije poput ``boot`` i "
"``casper``, a ne bi trebao biti prazan DVD koji sadrži .iso datoteku."

#: ../../burn.rst:52
msgid "In Linux"
msgstr "U Linuxu"

#: ../../burn.rst:53
msgid "Install and use ``xfburn``."
msgstr "Instalirajte i koristite ``xfburn``."

#: ../../burn.rst:56
msgid "In Windows"
msgstr "U Windowsima"

#: ../../burn.rst:57
msgid "Right-click the ISO file and select :menuselection:`Burn disk image`."
msgstr ""
"Desno kliknite na ISO datoteku i odaberite :menuselection:`Snimanje slike "
"diska`."

#: ../../burn.rst:59
msgid ""
"To make sure the ISO was burned without any errors, select "
":menuselection:`Verify disc after burning`."
msgstr ""
"Kako bi bili sigurni da je ISO slika snimljena bez grešaka, odaberite "
":menuselection:`Provjeri disk nakon snimanja`."

#: ../../burn.rst:62
msgid "In Mac OS"
msgstr "U Mac OS-u"

#: ../../burn.rst:63
msgid ""
"Right-click the ISO file and select :menuselection:`Burn Disk Image to Disc`."
msgstr ""
"Desno kliknite na ISO datoteku i odaberite :menuselection:`Burn Disk Image "
"to Disc`."

#: ../../choose.rst:2
msgid "Choose the right edition"
msgstr "Odabir željenog izdanja"

#: ../../choose.rst:4
msgid ""
"You can download Linux Mint from the `Linux Mint website "
"<https://linuxmint.com/download.php>`_."
msgstr ""
"Možete preuzeti Linux Mint s `Linux Mint web stranice "
"<https://linuxmint.com/download.php>`_."

#: ../../choose.rst:6
msgid ""
"Read below to choose which edition and architecture are right for you."
msgstr "Pročitajte ispod koje izdanje i arhitektura je prikladna za vas."

#: ../../choose.rst:9
msgid "Cinnamon, MATE or Xfce?"
msgstr "Cinnamon, MATE ili Xfce?"

#: ../../choose.rst:11
msgid ""
"Linux Mint comes in 3 different flavours, each featuring a different desktop "
"environment."
msgstr ""
"Linux Mint dolazi u 3 različita izdanja, svako sa drugačijim radnim "
"okruženjem."

#: ../../choose.rst:14 ../../choose.rst:26
msgid "Cinnamon"
msgstr "Cinnamon"

#: ../../choose.rst:14
msgid "The most modern, innovative and full-featured desktop"
msgstr "Najmodernija, inovativna i potpuna radna površina"

#: ../../choose.rst:15 ../../choose.rst:35
msgid "MATE"
msgstr "MATE"

#: ../../choose.rst:15
msgid "A more traditional, and faster desktop"
msgstr "Više tradicionalna i brža radna površina"

#: ../../choose.rst:16 ../../choose.rst:44
msgid "Xfce"
msgstr "Xfce"

#: ../../choose.rst:16
msgid "The most lightweight desktop"
msgstr "Najmanje zahtjevna radna površina"

#: ../../choose.rst:19
msgid ""
"The most popular version of Linux Mint is the Cinnamon edition. Cinnamon is "
"primarily developed for and by Linux Mint. It is slick, beautiful, and full "
"of new features."
msgstr ""
"Najpopularnije izdanje Linux Minta je Cinnamon izdanje. Cinnamon se "
"prvenstveno razvija za i od strane Linux Minta. Uglađen je, prekrasan i pun "
"novih značajki."

#: ../../choose.rst:28
msgid ""
"Linux Mint is also involved in the development of MATE, a classic desktop "
"environment which is the continuation of GNOME 2, Linux Mint's default "
"desktop between 2006 and 2011. Although it misses a few features and its "
"development is slower than Cinnamon's, MATE uses less resources and can run "
"faster on older computers."
msgstr ""
"Linux Mint je isto tako uključen u razvoj MATE-a, klasičnog radnog okruženja "
"koje je nastavak GNOMA 2, Linux Mintovog glavnog radnog okruženja između "
"2006 i 2011 god. Iako nedostaje nekoliko značajki i njegov razvoj je sporiji "
"nego Cinnamonov, MATE  koristi manje resursa i radi brže na starijim "
"računalima."

#: ../../choose.rst:37
msgid ""
"Xfce is a lightweight desktop environment. It doesn't support as many "
"features as Cinnamon or MATE, but it's extremely stable and very light on "
"resource usage."
msgstr ""
"Xfce je najmanje zahtjevno radno okruženje. Ne podržava tako mnogo značajki "
"kao Cinnamon ili MATE, ali je vrlo stabilan i vrlo malo troši resurse "
"sustava."

#: ../../choose.rst:46
msgid ""
"Of course, all three desktops are great and Linux Mint is extremely proud of "
"each edition. Although there are more features and better support in some "
"editions than others, and some do run faster and use less resources than "
"others, they're all great alternatives and choosing the right edition is "
"largely a matter of taste."
msgstr ""
"Naravno, sva tri radna okruženja su izvanredna i Linux Mint se vrlo ponosi "
"sa svakim od njih. Iako je u pojedinim više značajki i bolja podrška nego u "
"drugima, neki pak rade brže i troše manje resursa sustava od drugih, sva "
"okruženja su sjajna alternativa i odabir prikladnog izdanja je stvar ukusa "
"korisnika."

#: ../../choose.rst:48
msgid ""
"Other than their features and performance, Cinnamon, MATE and Xfce also "
"represent three different desktop environments, with different menus, "
"different panels and configuration tools. The right one for you is the one "
"where you feel at home."
msgstr ""
"Osim njihovih značajki i performansa, Cinnamon, MATE i Xfce isto tako "
"predstavljaju tri različita radna okruženja, s različitim izbornicima, "
"različitim panelima i alatima za podešavanje. Vama najprikladnije je ono s "
"kojim se osjećate kao da ste doma."

#: ../../choose.rst:50
msgid ""
"If you are unsure which desktop to choose start with the Cinnamon edition. "
"Try them all eventually when you have the time. All three of them have their "
"own audience within the Linux Mint community and they're all very popular."
msgstr ""
"Ako niste sigurni koju radnu površinu odabrati započnite s Cinnamon "
"izdanjem. Isprobajte ih sve kada imate vremena. Sva tri izdanja imaju svoju "
"publiku u Linux Mint zajednici i vrlo su popularni."

#: ../../choose.rst:54
msgid "32-bit or 64-bit?"
msgstr "32-bitna ili 64-bitna?"

#: ../../choose.rst:56
msgid "From version 20 onward, only 64-bit is available."
msgstr "Od izdanja 20 i novijeg, dostupno je samo 64-bitno izdanje."

#: ../../choose.rst:58
msgid ""
"The 32-bit ISO images on prior versions are provided for compatibility with "
"older computers. 32-bit processors are extremely rare nowadays and most "
"computers are able to run in 64-bit. If your computer was manufactured after "
"2007, you probably have a 64-bit processor."
msgstr ""
"32-bitne ISO slike na prijašnjim izdanjima se isporučuju zbog "
"kompatibilnosti sa starijim računalima. 32-bitni procesori danas su vrlo "
"rijetki i većina računala koristi 64-bitne procesore. Ako je vaše računalo "
"proizvedeno nakon 2007 godine, najvjerojatnije imate 64-bitni procesor."

#: ../../choose.rst:60
msgid ""
"If you have an old computer and you are unsure whether or not it can run in "
"64-bit, read `X86 Chronology "
"<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/X86#Chronology>`_."
msgstr ""
"Ako imate starije računalo i niste sigurni je li 64-bitno, pročitajte `X86 "
"Chronology <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/X86#Chronology>`_."

#: ../../choose.rst:63
msgid ""
"You can try to boot Linux Mint 64-bit on your computer. If it isn't "
"compatible, nothing bad will happen. You will just get an error message."
msgstr ""
"Možete pokušati pokrenuti 64-bitni Linux Mint na vašem računalu. Ako nije "
"kompatibilan, ništa loše se neće učiniti. Samo ćete vidjeti poruku o grešci."

#: ../../choose.rst:66
msgid ""
"If you cannot boot or install Linux Mint because your hardware is too recent "
"and is not properly detected see the `Edge ISO Images <https://linuxmint-"
"user-guide.readthedocs.io/en/latest/edge.html>`_ chapter in the Linux Mint "
"User Guide for an alternative ISO."
msgstr ""
"Ako ne možete pokrenuti ili instalirati Linux Mint zato jer imate najnoviji "
"hardver koji nije ispravno otkriven pogledajte `Edge ISO slike "
"<https://linuxmint-user-guide.readthedocs.io/en/latest/edge.html>`_ "
"poglavlje u Linux Mint korisničkom priručniku za alternativne ISO slike."

#: ../../codecs.rst:2
msgid "Multimedia codecs"
msgstr "Multimedijski kôdeki"

#: ../../codecs.rst:4
msgid "Some multimedia content requires additional codecs to be installed."
msgstr ""
"Određeni multimedijski sadržaj zahtijeva instalaciju dodatnih kôdeka."

#: ../../codecs.rst:7
msgid ""
"If you were online when installing Linux Mint and you ticked the option to "
"install these codecs, they are already installed."
msgstr ""
"Ako ste bili povezani sa internetom tijekom instalacije Linux Minta i "
"odabrali ste mogućnost instalacije tih kôdeka, oni su već instalirani."

#: ../../codecs.rst:9
msgid ""
"Launch :menuselection:`Menu --> Sound & Video --> Install Multimedia Codecs`."
msgstr ""
"Pokrenite :menuselection:`Izbornik --> Zvuk i video --> Instaliraj "
"multimedijske kôdeke`."

#: ../../codecs.rst:14
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Install`."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Instaliraj`."

#: ../../codecs.rst:16
msgid ""
"Enter your password and wait for the codecs to be installed on your computer."
msgstr ""
"Upišite svoju lozinku i pričekajte dok se kôdeki ne instaliraju na vaše "
"računalo."

#: ../../drivers.rst:2
msgid "Hardware drivers"
msgstr "Hardverski upravljački programi"

#: ../../drivers.rst:4
msgid ""
"One of the first things to do after installing Linux Mint is to check for "
"available hardware drivers."
msgstr ""
"Jedna od prvih stvari nakon instalacije Linux Minta je provjera dostupnosti "
"hardverskih upravljačkih programa."

#: ../../drivers.rst:6
msgid "Launch :menuselection:`Menu --> Administration --> Driver Manager`."
msgstr ""
"Pokrenite :menuselection:`Izbornik --> Administracija --> Upravitelj "
"upravljačkih programa`."

#: ../../drivers.rst:13
msgid ""
"If you are offline, the Driver Manager will complain that it cannot connect "
"to the Internet."
msgstr ""
"Ako nemate pristup internetu, Upravitelj upravljačkih programa će vas "
"upozoriti da se ne može povezati sa internetom."

#: ../../drivers.rst:19
msgid ""
"Insert your bootable Linux Mint USB stick (or DVD), wait for it to be "
"mounted, and click :guilabel:`OK`."
msgstr ""
"Umetnite svoj USB uređaj ili DVD za pokretanje Linux Mint sustava, "
"pričekajte da se montira, i klinite :guilabel:`U redu`."

#: ../../drivers.rst:21
msgid ""
"Tick the appropriate checkboxes to select the available drivers and click "
":guilabel:`Apply Changes`."
msgstr ""
"Označite prikladnu mogućnost za odabir dostupnih upravljačkih programa i "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Primijeni promjene`."

#: ../../efi.rst:2
msgid "EFI"
msgstr "EFI"

#: ../../efi.rst:5
msgid "SecureBoot"
msgstr "SecureBoot"

#: ../../efi.rst:7
msgid ""
"If after installing Linux Mint in EFI mode, you are unable to boot due to a "
"``Secure Boot Violation``, you can try one of the following solutions:"
msgstr ""
"Ako nakon instalacije Linux Minta u EFI načinu, ne možete pokrenuti sustav "
"uslijed ``Secure Boot Violation``, možete probati jedno od sljedećih "
"rješenja:"

#: ../../efi.rst:15
msgid "Restart the installation:"
msgstr "Ponovno pokrenite instalaciju:"

#: ../../efi.rst:14
msgid "Connect to the Internet before the installation"
msgstr "Povežite se sa internetom prije instalacije"

#: ../../efi.rst:15
msgid ""
"**Do not** select ``Install third-party software for graphics and Wi-Fi "
