#: ../../locales.rst:4
msgid ""
"Language support includes translations but also packages related to spell-"
"checking, synonyms, hyphenation and dictionaries which enhance your "
"experience in software applications such as LibreOffice."
msgstr ""
"Jezična podrška uključuje prijevode, ali i pakete koji se odnose na provjeru "
"pravopisa, sinonime, spojnice i rječnike koji poboljšavaju vaše iskustvo u "
"softverskim aplikacijama poput LibreOffica."

#: ../../locales.rst:6
msgid "Launch :menuselection:`Menu --> Preferences --> Languages`."
msgstr "Pokrenite :menuselection:`Izbornik --> Postavke --> Jezici`."

#: ../../locales.rst:12
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Install / Remove Language`."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Instaliraj / Ukloni jezike...`."

#: ../../locales.rst:18
msgid ""
"If beside your locale, you see a label saying ``Some language packs are "
"missing``, select your locale and click :guilabel:`Install language packs`."
msgstr ""
"Ako pokraj vašeg jezika, vidite natpis ``Neki jezični paketi nedostaju``, "
"odaberite svoj jezik i kliknite :guilabel:`Instaliraj jezični paket`."

#: ../../multiboot.rst:2
msgid "Multi-boot"
msgstr "Pokretanje više operativih sustava"

#: ../../multiboot.rst:5
msgid "Always install Windows first"
msgstr "Uvijek prvo instalirajte Windowse"

#: ../../multiboot.rst:7
msgid ""
"Windows does not detect other operating systems and does not feature a boot "
"menu. When you install it, it overwrites your boot sequence and your "
"computer then boots straight into Windows."
msgstr ""
"Windowsi ne otkrivaju druge operativne sustave i ne sadrže izbornik "
"pokretanja sustava. Kada ih instalirate, prebrisuju vaš poredak pokretanja i "
"vaše računalo se tada pokreće izravno u Windows."

#: ../../multiboot.rst:9
msgid ""
"Linux Mint (and most Linux distributions) detects other operating systems "
"and builds a menu from which you can choose which system to boot."
msgstr ""
"Linux Mint (i većina Linux distribucija) otkrivaju druge operativne sustave "
"i stvaraju izbornik iz kojeg odabirete željeni operativni sustav za "
"pokretanje."

#: ../../multiboot.rst:11
msgid ""
"For this reason, if you want to dual-boot or multi-boot with Windows, it is "
"easier and recommended to install Windows first, before you install Linux "
"Mint."
msgstr ""
"Stoga, ako želite dualno pokretanje ili pokretanje više operativnih sustava "
"s Windowsima, lakše je i preporučljivo prvo instalirati Windows, a nakon "
"njih Linux Mint."

#: ../../multiboot.rst:14
msgid "Fix the boot sequence"
msgstr "Popravak poredka pokretanja"

#: ../../multiboot.rst:16
msgid "If Windows overwrites your boot sequence:"
msgstr "Ako Windowsi prebrišu vaš poredak pokretanja:"

#: ../../multiboot.rst:22
